Package: autoSTK
Type: Package
Title: Automatic Spatio-Temporal Kriging
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Insang", "Song", email = "geoissong@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8732-3256"))
    )
Description: Automatic spatio-temporal Kriging extending the automap package
    (Hiemstra et al. 2010). Provides automatic variogram model fitting with
    multiple optimisers (L-BFGS-B with multi-start, LHS grid search), covariance
    structure selection via AIC/BIC or cross-validation, and spatiotemporal
    prediction via gstat. Four cross-validation strategies for spatiotemporal
    data are implemented.
